### Output Format

The color that results after any adjustments can be output in the
selected Output Format. The full list of output formats is NetLogo
Number, NetLogo word and RGBA (Red, Green, Blue, Alpha). However in some
contexts only a NetLogo Number can be output. As the user changes a
color the value of the Input value is updated. In the image below it was
initially lime - 0.3, but changed to lime - 0.6

